= cali

Interactive cal(1) (but the name ical was taken)

== Usage

 pip install cali
 cali
 # interactive session

 cat > ~/dates <<END
 2010-09-01 Write a better README for cali
 2010-09-02 ...
 2010-09-03 Profit
 END

 cali ~/dates
 # interactive session with calendar entries

 mkdir -p ~/.config/cali
 cat > ~/.config/cali/config <<END
 [DEFAULT]
 dates = ~/dates
 END

 cali
 # interactive session with calendar entries

== Screenshots

 bin/cali README.rdoc

    September 2010
